      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented regression test suite covering blood-flow constitutive models; formal change control process.",
      "rationale": "Solver is version-controlled and regression tests exist for general fluid dynamics. However, hemolysis-specific regression tests are absent and no formal change control process is documented for constitutive model updates. Achieved level 2 against required level 4 at MRL 5."
