      "rationale": "Four of five operating points match COU envelope within stated tolerances. Low-flow high-speed condition (2 L/min, 3600 RPM) not represented in validation dataset; extrapolation required. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., NMSE or E_rel) below 10% for hemolysis index at all operating points; statistical significance assessed.",
      "rationale": "Relative error below 18% at 4 of 5 conditions; one outlier at 22%. No statistical significance testing performed; single experimental replicate available for three conditions. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
