      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation geometry is the FDA generic centrifugal pump; operating conditions span the full COU envelope; blood analogue properties match clinical hematocrit range.",
      "rationale": "Validation geometry matches FDA generic pump. Operating conditions cover 4 of 5 COU points. Blood analogue (glycerol-water mixture) used in experiments rather than porcine blood; viscosity matched but viscoelastic effects not captured. Achieved level 3 against required level 5."
    },
