    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors reviewed. Seven factors assessed with achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5; six factors not assessed due to data unavailability. Monte Carlo UQ performed but input coverage insufficient. Despite gaps, the assessment package is accepted as complete documentation of the current credibility state for regulatory submission purposes, with noted deficiencies to be addressed in subsequent assessment cycle.",
